txt.en: You have discovered trap-door spiders dwelling along the Winding Stair, waiting to ambush anyone who passes by. Defeat these ambush predators before they claim any further victims.
Trap-door spiders make their home along the Winding Stair, waiting to ambush anyone who passes by.
You have successfully cleared the stair of ambushing spiders, which will allow the Rangers of Ithilien safe passage in the future.
Trap-door ambushers can be found along the Winding Stair in Cirith Ungol.\n\nYou should defeat trap-door ambushers.
